Package com.appygram.java

Interface Summary
AppygramEventHandler Handles the AppygramEvent once an Appygram is sent.
 

Class Summary
Appygram Main class used for configuring and accessing AppygramMessengers.
AppygramConfig Set initial properties for sending appygrams.
AppygramEvent An event for when Appygrams are sent.
AppygramLogger Handles all Appygram logging.
AppygramMessage Represents an Appygram message.
AppygramMessenger Handles delivery of messages and traces, as well as grabs the topic list.
AppygramTopic Represents a topic set up on Appygram.com.
AppygramTopicList Represents an list of AppygramTopics.
AppygramTrace Represents an Appygram message specifically for handling exceptions.
AppygramTraceData Trace information about an exception, handles serializing stack trace information into Appygram trace format.
